  "slug": "kokshanian-v-spectrum-securities-et-al",
  "status": "publish",
  "type": "page",
  "link": "https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/success\/kokshanian-v-spectrum-securities-et-al\/",
  "title": { "rendered": "Kokshanian v. Spectrum Securities" },
  "content": {
    "rendered": "<div id=\"pl-462\" class=\"panel-layout\">\n<div id=\"pg-462-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-462-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\">\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/iStock-882437642_1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-3045\" src=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/iStock-882437642_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"532\" height=\"266\" srcset=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/iStock-882437642_1.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/iStock-882437642_1-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/iStock-882437642_1-768x384.jpg 768w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/iStock-882437642_1-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/iStock-882437642_1-960x480.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 532px) 100vw, 532px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p id=\"panel-462-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\"><span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\">Our client was employed as a bus mechanic with the City of  Fresno. He went to the defendant&#8217;s stock brokerage house and was induced by a broker to invest his life savings of $30,000 in three highly speculative limited partnerships involving a cosmetic store chain. The client lost all of his money. This action was brought before the NASD to compel the defendants to pay our client the monies he lost.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pg-462-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-462-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-462-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<p>The broker\u2019s liability was predicated on negligence and the firm\u2019s liability was predicated on a failure to supervise the broker. After an arbitration hearing, the three-member NASD panel awarded our client the sum of $40,000. The award was then entered as a judgment against the defendants.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pgc-462-1-1\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-462-1-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n",
    "protected": false
  },
  "excerpt": {
    "rendered": "<p>Our client was employed as a bus mechanic with the City of  Fresno. He went to the defendant&#8217;s stock brokerage house and was induced by a broker to invest his life savings of $30,000 in three highly speculative limited partnerships involving a cosmetic store chain. The client lost all of his money. This action was brought before the NASD to compel the defendants to pay our client the monies he lost. The broker\u2019s liability was predicated on negligence and the firm\u2019s liability was predicated on a failure to supervise the broker. After an arbitration hearing, the three-member NASD panel&#8230;<\/p>\n",
    "protected": false
  },
